             was indicted for <rs id="t18080601-39-off216" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18080601-39-off216" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080601-39-off216" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18080601-39-cd217" type="crimeDate">19th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080601-39-off216 t18080601-39-cd217"></join>, three shirts, value 7 s. and a shawl, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18080601-39-victim356" type="victimName">
                     Benjamin 
                     Bond
                  <interp inst="t18080601-39-victim356" type="surname" value="Bond"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080601-39-victim356" type="given" value="Benjamin"></interp>
