                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080601-39-defend354 t18080601-39-punish222"></join>
               Fined One Shilling
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
